item.title: How to set msi mystic light rgb
item.description: If you use msi as your computer, you can change the color setting as follow it. Download MSI Center https://www.msi.com/Landing/mystic-light-rgb-gaming-pc/download Install Mystic Light from feature set You can select color and style as you like. Of course, you can always turn off light.
